node.text: First look at Nude Suede — a moody, sensual scent with sultry notes of ylang ylang and tuberose. Make it yours on 9.2.

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by KKW FRAGRANCE on August 24, 2021. May be an image of saddle-stitched leather.

node.text:
Introducing Essential Nudes

Nude Sand - Delicate notes of baie rose and peony are met with a heady blend of tonka bean and ambrette to create a soft, sophisticated scent.

Nude Silk - A fresh and gentle balance of balmy florals, lush green leaves and juicy peach nectar inspire this radiant, feminine fragrance.

Nude Soleil - A warm essence of vetiver, santal accord, and honeysuckle envelop the senses and meet the skin with a golden, glowing aroma.

Nude Suede - A velvety, textured mix of white amber and rich patchouli, paired with light, crisp notes of white grapefruit and vintage jasmine.

Launching Thursday, 9.2 at 12PM PT #EssentialNudes
